<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Complete Your Account Setup</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: #2c3e50; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 20px; background: #f9f9f9; }
        .button { display: inline-block; background: #3498db; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .footer { padding: 20px; text-align: center; color: #666; font-size: 14px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="header">
        <h1>üåç Migrantifly</h1>
        <h2>Complete Your Account Setup</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Dear {{clientName}},</p>

        <p>Thank you for choosing Migrantifly for your immigration journey! Following our consultation, you can now complete your account setup to begin your visa application process.</p>

        <p><strong>Next Steps:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>Create your secure password</li>
            <li>Complete your profile information</li>
            <li>Sign the service agreement</li>
            <li>Make your deposit payment</li>
            <li>Upload required documents</li>
        </ul>

        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="{{setupLink}}" class="button">Complete Account Setup</a>
        </div>

        <p><strong>Visa Pathways Discussed:</strong></p>
        {{#each visaPathways}}
            <li>{{this}}</li>
        {{/each}}

        <p>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>¬© 2025 Migrantifly Immigration Services | Auckland, New Zealand</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>